<% content_for :title, "Privacy Policy — Allimgtools" %>

<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p class="text-base-content/40 text-sm mb-10">Last updated: <%= Date.new(2026, 4, 14).strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></p>

  <div class="prose prose-sm max-w-none space-y-8">

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">1. Who We Are</h2>
      <p class="text-base-content/70 leading-relaxed">
        Allimgtools (<a href="https://allimgtools.com" class="underline hover:text-base-content">allimgtools.com</a>) provides free online image processing tools.
        This policy explains what personal data we collect, why we collect it, and your rights under the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and other applicable laws.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">2. What We Collect and Why</h2>

      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="bg-base-200 rounded-xl p-4">
          <p class="font-medium text-sm mb-1">Account Information (Google Sign-In)</p>
          <p class="text-base-content/70 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            When you sign in with Google, we receive your name, email address, and profile picture from Google.
            This data is used solely to identify your account.
          </p>
          <p class="text-base-content/50 text-xs mt-1.5">
            Legal basis: Performance of a contract (providing account-based features).
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-base-200 rounded-xl p-4">
          <p class="font-medium text-sm mb-1">Uploaded Images</p>
          <p class="text-base-content/70 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Images you upload are processed on our servers for the sole purpose of completing the task you requested (e.g. compress, resize, convert).
            Files are automatically deleted within 3 hours. We do not analyze, store permanently, or share your images.
          </p>
          <p class="text-base-content/50 text-xs mt-1.5">
            Legal basis: Performance of a contract (processing your image as requested).
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-base-200 rounded-xl p-4">
          <p class="font-medium text-sm mb-1">Usage Analytics (Google Analytics)</p>
          <p class="text-base-content/70 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            We use Google Analytics to understand how visitors use the site (page views, traffic sources, etc.).
            This data is aggregated and anonymous. Google Analytics may set cookies on your browser.
          </p>
          <p class="text-base-content/50 text-xs mt-1.5">
            Legal basis: Legitimate interest (improving the service). EU/EEA users will be asked for consent via a cookie banner before Analytics is loaded.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">3. What We Don't Do</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-base-content/70">
        <li>We do not sell your personal data to third parties</li>
        <li>We do not use your data for advertising or profiling</li>
        <li>We do not share your images with anyone</li>
        <li>We do not use your email to send marketing messages</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">4. Third-Party Services</h2>
      <p class="text-base-content/70 leading-relaxed mb-3">
        We use the following third-party services, each governed by their own privacy policies:
      </p>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-base-content/70 text-sm">
        <li>
          <span class="font-medium">Google OAuth</span> —
          Used for sign-in. See <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="underline hover:text-base-content">Google's Privacy Policy</a>.
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="font-medium">Google Analytics</span> —
          Used for anonymous usage statistics. See <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="underline hover:text-base-content">Google's Privacy Policy</a>.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">5. Data Retention</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-1 text-base-content/70 text-sm">
        <li><span class="font-medium">Uploaded files</span> — deleted automatically within 3 hours of processing.</li>
        <li><span class="font-medium">Account data</span> — retained while your account is active. Deleted upon request.</li>
        <li><span class="font-medium">Analytics data</span> — retained by Google per their standard retention settings.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">6. Your Rights</h2>
      <p class="text-base-content/70 leading-relaxed mb-2">
        Under GDPR (and similar laws), you have the right to:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-base-content/70">
        <li><span class="font-medium">Access</span> — request a copy of the personal data we hold about you</li>
        <li><span class="font-medium">Rectification</span> — ask us to correct inaccurate data</li>
        <li><span class="font-medium">Erasure</span> — request deletion of your account and associated data</li>
        <li><span class="font-medium">Objection</span> — object to processing based on legitimate interest (e.g. Analytics)</li>
        <li><span class="font-medium">Portability</span> — receive your data in a machine-readable format</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-base-content/70 leading-relaxed mt-3">
        To exercise any of these rights, please contact us. We will respond within 30 days.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p class="text-base-content/70 leading-relaxed">
        We may update this policy as the service evolves. When we do, we will update the "Last updated" date at the top of this page.
        Continued use of the service after changes are posted constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">8. Contact</h2>
      <p class="text-base-content/70 leading-relaxed">
        For any privacy-related questions or requests, please contact us via the contact information available on our website.
      </p>
    </section>

  </div>
</div>
